item.title: In conversation with Dr Zara Benjamin-Laing
item.description: We had a chat with Dr Zara to discover what a day in the life at Birmingham hospital amid the coronavirus pandemic. Image: Zara Benjamin-Laing Dr Zara Benjamin-Laing is a Senior House Officer (SHO) currently working in Birmingham.
